description:
Danny is back from time with his family to recap this week's The Real Housewives of Beverly Hills and The Real Housewives of New York. On Bev Hills, the women are still in Tahoe, playing Jenga and having dinners. On New York, Heather and Leah are still at odds and it all comes to a blow in the bus. Also, we finally find out what Luann's baton is for!


RHONY Recap: 33:28ish
